OL,3,CConsumer confidence 'collapses' as
OL,4,CMiddle East war escalates
OL,6,FConsumer confidence has "collapsed" as
OL,7,Fthe war in the Middle East raises
OL,8,Ffears of soaring inflation over the
OL,9,Fcoming months, figures show.
OL,11,FThe British Retail Consortium (BRC)
OL,12,Fsurvey by Opinium, taken between March
OL,13,F10 and March 13, shows consumer
OL,14,Fexpectations of the economy over the
OL,15,Fnext three months fell to its lowest
OL,16,Flevel on record, plunging to minus 53
OL,17,Ffrom minus 30 in February.
OL,19,FExpectations for personal finances
OL,20,Falso fell to a record low of minus 17,
OL,21,Fdown from minus six in February.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@cO]
